data.description: Embrace the Royal Life in this Grand 6-Bedroom, 3.5-Bathroom Palace! Step into the land of endless possibilities with this grand 6-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom palace that's larger than your dreams and cozier than a corner seat at a coffee shop! With 4,070 sqft of pure enchantment, get ready to embrace your inner royalty.    This home doesn't just have a back patio – it has a COVERED back patio that's practically the VIP lounge for sunsets, BBQs, and spontaneous dance parties. Need room for your royal carriages? No worries, there's a 3-car garage. And let's talk about it being a corner lot, shall we? With 6 bedrooms, you'll never run out of spaces to claim as your own. The primary suite is fit for a monarch, complete with an en-suite bathroom that's basically your personal spa getaway. Upstairs you'll find a game room that's so spacious, it could host a mini board games tournament. Whether you're into video games or just creating epic dance-offs, this game room has got you covered.
